ShipInfoData.name: REFLECTION
ShipInfoData.description: Celebrity Reflection received several new enhancements during her recent dry dock. Now, you can experience a cinematic night under the stars with A Taste of Film at the Rooftop Terrace. It's an exciting way to enjoy the great outdoors, satisfy your love of movies, and dazzle your taste buds all at once
